Class FeatureGraphGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aksw.simba.lemming.creation.FeatureGraphGenerator

  • public class FeatureGraphGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements algorithms for generating coloured graphs according to a given set of features, namely coloured degree distributions and edge colour distributions
    Author:
    Jonas Hanselle (jmhansel@campus.uni-paderborn.de)
